DEPRECATED — Legacy Migration Chain
====================================

This migration directory is a LEGACY chain and MUST NOT be extended with new
migrations. The canonical Alembic migration system lives at the project root:

    alembic/          (canonical)
    alembic.ini       (canonical config)

Both chains target the same database.db, so adding migrations to both creates
schema conflict risk (R2-01).

Existing migrations here (b609a11e13cc, 5d5764ef9f26) are kept for historical
schema tracking but should not be run independently. All future schema changes
MUST go through the root alembic/ directory.
